

1 Am ant si i ni-oidahim k hab i ni-ah mantki pi am hu wo i em-chehgim hemu manis wo ge s-em-kehꞌel. 2 Mt pi wo ap e taht mantp hab wo ni-juh. Nt ahni hab waꞌap pi wo ap ni-taht. 3 Heg ant hekaj am wabsh em-oꞌohani. Ab amt wo chum ni-mah g s-ap tahhadkam. Kuni pi tatchua manis am wo chum jiwia em-wui k wabsh pi wo ap ni-taht em-wehhejed. S-mahch ani mamt wo s-hehgigk mant hekid ahni wo s-hehgigk. 4 Si ani pi ap ni-tahtk ch muꞌi ni-ohꞌog iawua am em-oꞌohanidk nani pi si pihk ni-elid em-hekaj. Ni eda pi tatchua manis ab wo em-mah g pi ap tahhadkam. 

**Mat ab wo i s-hoꞌigeꞌel hegai mat wo dagito g e-chuꞌijig **

5 Ab at i em-mah g pi ap tahhadkam hegai mat am si pi ap has chuꞌi em-shahgid. Kuni pi tatchua manis ab wabsh wo si em-chehmo. 6 Am at wa geꞌe ab nako g e-namkidadag ab em-amjed mamt has i masma am apꞌech. 7 Mt hahawa ab wo i s-hoꞌigeꞌid k ab wo i gewkemhu nat pi has e juh k am hu wo si pi ap e tahtam k wabsh si s-wohom gm hu hab wo i e juh. 8 Am g dahm ep wo ahgid mam ab si pihk e elid wui. 9 S-mahchimk ani am i em-oꞌohanidk mams ab wo s-ni-wohog el. Kumt wa woho am hab e juh. 10 Kunt hab waꞌap ab wo i s-hoꞌigeꞌel hegai mat pi ap has chuꞌi mamtp ahpim ab wo i s-hoꞌigeꞌel. 11 T hab pi wo e nako g Jiawul mas wo t-wohppoꞌi ihda t-wehnag. S-mahch ach mo hab wa s-e junimk. 

**Matsh g Paul wehpeg e kudut k ab hahawa bei g s-hehgig **

12 Pegih, nt wa pi am hu em-wui hih am himadch Macedonia wui k wabshaba am hih Troas wui. Tki g Jiosh am apꞌech mant am i ahgachug g haꞌichu ahgaj amai. 13 Nt am hu hebai ni-kudu nat pi pi oi jiwia g Titus am i em-chehgimedk. Kunt am i ha hoꞌigeꞌel g t-wehm wohochuddam amai k gam hu hih Macedonia wui. T am ni-nam g Titus k am ni-ahgid mamt s-ap am hab juh g ni-neꞌoki. 

14 Kuni heg amjed ab si ihm g Jiosh mat am i apꞌech hegai mo pi apꞌe am em-shahgid. Jiosh o chum hekid ab t-mahkch g gewitoidag hekaj hegai mat g Christ am t-wehhejed hab juh. Haꞌichu t-ahga ab amjed g Christ o an wehsko e gantan hab sha masma mat g s-ap uhwchu wehsko wo e hewagi mat hebai wo e mehi. 15-16 Hegam mat wo e doꞌibia o ab si s-hohhoꞌid ch kah mo g Jiosh ab ha makiog g pi ha huhugedam doakag. K hegam mat pi wo e doꞌibia pi hohhoꞌid ch kah mo am hihim pi ha huhugedam muhkig wui. Pegih, do si s-has haꞌichu chikpan ihda. 17 Kut pi wo e nako mat am hab wo juh hegam mo wabsh pehegichud g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch wabsh s-uꞌimk g lial. Ahchim Christ pionag ach hi pi hab shaꞌi masma ch pi em-iattogid ch wabshaba s-ap am ahgachug ihda wohokam mo g Jiosh ab t-mahkch. 

